# ai-dev-kit workflow

Before non-trivial work in this project:

1. Read `.ai/STATE.md` (workflow cursor), `.ai/PROJECT.md` (charter), and `.ai/kit/CONVENTIONS.md` (house rules).
2. Resolve prompts in this order: `.ai/overrides/<path>` first, then `.ai/kit/prompts/<path>`.
3. When unsure which prompt to run, load `.ai/kit/prompts/meta/route.md`.
4. Before ending a session, use `.ai/kit/prompts/meta/session-wrap.md` — the only safe stopping point.

Do not edit files under `.ai/kit/`. Port kit changes upstream to the ai-dev-kit repository and bump the pinned version.
